						               													<description>Hero Dice is a dice-based competitive role-playing game where every player is vying to become the most famous Hero around. Roll your character race, class and ability, and then set out exploring dungeons, fighting bandits, and showing up other Heroes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the start of you the game every player rolls to determine their Race, Class, and Ability. They will play a factor in battles against other players and enemies you encounter, providing advantages and disadvantages. As you roll other dice throughout the game, if you hit one of your 3 main die, it will automatically change to reflect the new die face up - only you can change your character.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game you'll be earning Fame and Infamy which can be spent to help you succeed at battles and gaining Companions. Though there's a lot of randomness to be had with dice, it involves a great deal of strategy and provides multiple ways to play and experience the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In a quest to become the most famous Hero around, how will you get there? Honor, deception, friendship, treachery...what kind of Hero will you become?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
